description: Firm appointment scheduled with specific date/time confirmed, address collected, customer committed
business_impact: Highest revenue potential ($24-$58). Best possible outcome.

description: Customer engaged and interested but didn't book immediately. Said will call back, check with spouse, etc.
business_impact: Medium revenue potential ($9-$27). May convert later.

description: Customer got information but unlikely to convert. Warranty questions, price checking only.
business_impact: Low revenue potential. Unlikely conversion.

description: Buyer/agent disconnected call prematurely (<30s). Technical issues or refused to help.
business_impact: Lost opportunity. Buyer-side issue.
action_required: Flag to buyer, review call quality

description: Consumer/caller disconnected prematurely (<30s). Wrong number, frustrated, accidental.
business_impact: Lost opportunity. Traffic quality issue.

description: Buyer explicitly refused to provide service despite consumer wanting help. Zero value provided.
business_impact: Should not be billed. Clear quality issue.
action_required: Dispute if billed, flag buyer performance

description: Consumer intended to reach different company/brand. Expected in brand bidding campaigns.
business_impact: DATA POINT ONLY - NOT a dispute trigger. Can still be billable if buyer engages.
action_required: Track for brand campaign ROI analysis

description: Buyer cannot service customer's location. Outside service territory.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Clear quality issue. Should not be billed.
action_required: Dispute immediately, add ZIP to exclusion list after 5+ occurrences

description: Buyer does not service TVs. Wrong vertical match.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Clear quality issue. Should not be billed.

description: Buyer does not service commercial equipment. Wrong vertical match.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Clear quality issue. Should not be billed.

description: Buyer does not service HVAC. Wrong vertical match.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Clear quality issue. Should not be billed.

description: Buyer does not service pool equipment. Wrong vertical match.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Clear quality issue. Should not be billed.

description: Buyer does not service this appliance type. Wrong vertical match.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Clear quality issue. Should not be billed.

description: No agents available / buyer closed during stated business hours. Staffing problem.
business_impact: Lost opportunity. Buyer's fault - campaign configured per their schedule.
action_required: Flag to buyer about availability issues. Do NOT adjust routing.

description: Technical problem on buyer's end. Call dropped, transfer failed, IVR stuck 60+ seconds.
business_impact: Lost opportunity. Buyer's fault - technical issues.
action_required: Flag to buyer about technical issues

description: Call duration <10 seconds. No meaningful conversation possible.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Never billable. Clear quality issue.

description: Soft flag for borderline situations. Buyer recognized prior contact, 30-60s unclear value.
business_impact: Potential dispute risk. Needs review if buyer disputes.
action_required: Flag for review, do NOT auto-dispute

description: Emergency situation. Appliance completely broken. Needs immediate service.
business_impact: Highest conversion probability. Priority lead.

description: No emergency. Appliance still working but having issues. Wants checkup.
business_impact: Lower urgency. May take longer to convert.

description: Customer believes appliance is under warranty. Looking for free service.
business_impact: 50/50 conversion. Can convert to paid repair if out of warranty.
action_required: Track warranty vs paid repair conversion rates

description: Getting quotes from multiple providers. Focused on cost. Not ready to book.
business_impact: Medium conversion. Normal lead gen behavior.

description: Weighing repair cost vs buying new appliance. May not repair at all.
business_impact: 50/50 conversion. Track for targeting optimization.
action_required: Analyze repair vs replace decision patterns

description: Consumer looking to purchase parts, not repair service. Wants DIY.
business_impact: Low conversion. Wrong type of lead for repair services.

description: Washing machine repair needed. Common issues: unbalanced, leaking, won't spin.
business_impact: High conversion rate. Necessary appliance.

description: Dryer repair needed. Common issues: not heating, not turning, takes too long.
business_impact: High conversion rate. Necessary appliance.

description: Refrigerator/freezer repair needed. Common issues: not cooling, ice maker, compressor.
business_impact: HIGHEST conversion rate. Emergency - food spoilage risk.

description: Dishwasher repair needed. Common issues: not cleaning, not draining, door issues.
business_impact: Medium conversion rate. Less critical appliance.

description: Oven/stove/range repair needed. Common issues: not heating, burner, igniter.
business_impact: Medium-High conversion rate.

description: Microwave repair needed. Common issues: not heating, turntable, sparking.
business_impact: Low conversion rate. Cheap to replace.

description: Garbage disposal repair needed. Common issues: jammed, leaking, grinding.
business_impact: Medium conversion rate.

description: Customer mentions 2+ appliances needing service.
business_impact: Variable. Could be higher ticket value.

description: Cannot determine appliance type from transcript.
business_impact: Quality concern. Transcript may be unclear.

description: Buyer does not service this appliance type (TV).
business_impact: $0 revenue. Wrong vertical.

description: Buyer does not service this appliance type (HVAC).
business_impact: $0 revenue. Wrong vertical.

description: Buyer does not service this appliance type (other).
business_impact: $0 revenue. Wrong vertical.

description: Duration >60s meaningful conversation OR appointment scheduled OR detailed qualification.
business_impact: $9-$58 revenue expected. Approve billing.

description: Duration 40-60s with unclear outcome. Partial qualification. Review if disputed.
business_impact: $0-$27 revenue possible. May be disputed.

description: Duration <40s OR major quality flag OR NO_BUYER_INTEREST. Should not be billed.
business_impact: $0 revenue. Dispute if currently billed.

description: Customer age 65+, needs assistance, mentions mobility issues.
business_impact: High lifetime value. May need accessible service.
action_required: Track buyer performance with elderly customers

description: Landlord/property manager with rental or investment property.
business_impact: Very high lifetime value. Repeat business potential.

description: Inexperienced with repairs. Lots of basic questions. Needs guidance.
business_impact: Standard value. May need more hand-holding.

description: Language barriers evident. ESL, heavy accent, communication challenges.
business_impact: Standard value. May need bilingual buyer.
action_required: Route to appropriate buyers if available

description: Business location - restaurant, hotel, laundromat. Multiple units.
business_impact: High ticket value. Specialized needs.

description: Professional, helpful, asked qualifying questions, attempted to close effectively.
business_impact: Positive correlation with conversion. Route more calls.
action_required: Increase call allocation to this buyer

description: Rude, dismissive, unprofessional, didn't attempt to help.
business_impact: Negative correlation with conversion. Lost opportunities.
action_required: Review with buyer, consider reducing allocation

description: Customer ready to book but buyer didn't ask. Gave up easily on objections.
business_impact: Lost potential revenue. Training opportunity.
action_required: Flag for buyer training, review performance

description: Clear ready-to-buy signals. Urgent need. Decision-maker on call.
business_impact: Best traffic source. Highest conversion rate.
action_required: Optimize for more of this traffic

description: Thought they were calling manufacturer. Googled brand name.
business_impact: EXPECTED in brand campaigns. Can still convert well.
action_required: Track for brand campaign ROI analysis

description: Consumer mentions calling other companies. Has appointment elsewhere.
business_impact: NORMAL lead gen behavior - NOT a problem. Still billable if buyer engages.

description: Customer tried fixing themselves, made it worse, watched YouTube videos.
business_impact: May be more complex repair (higher ticket value). Customer already invested effort.

description: Insurance is involved. Needs documentation. Flood/fire/damage mentioned.
business_impact: Different timeline and process. May need specialized handling.

description: Looking to purchase parts only, not repair service. DIY intent.
business_impact: Wrong type of lead for repair services. Low conversion.

description: Weighing repair vs replacement. May not convert to repair.
business_impact: 50/50 conversion. Track for targeting optimization.

description: Staffing/hours problem. No agents available. Closed during business hours.
business_impact: Lost opportunity. Buyer's fault - their schedule.
action_required: Flag to buyer. Do NOT adjust routing.

description: Technical issues. Call drops, transfers fail, IVR problems.
business_impact: Lost opportunity. Buyer's fault - technical.
action_required: Flag to buyer about technical issues
